.TP
\fB\-\-linger\fR
do not shut down the container on exit
.TP
\fB\-\-option\fR, \fB\-O\fR OPTION
key=value option for the build. See `\-O list` for a
list of available option for each build style
.TP
\fB\-\-quick\fR
quild quickly, assuming the container is up to date
