.TP
\fB\-w\fR, \fB\-\-workdir\fR WORKDIR
bind mount (writable) the given directory as working
directory
.TP
\fB\-W\fR, \fB\-\-workdir\-volatile\fR WORKDIR_VOLATILE
bind mount (volatile) the given directory as working
directory
.TP
\fB\-\-clone\fR repository
